Caixa Won’t Accept Bidvest’s Takeover Offer for Its Mercantile Bank Unit

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-07-06T15:10:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/caixa-won-t-accept-bidvest-s-takeover-offer-for-its-mercantile-bank-unit.html
Mercantile Bank Holdings Ltd. (MTL)  said
the board of directors of its controlling shareholder Caixa
Geral De Depositas SA will not provide support for a takeover
offer for Mercantile from  Bidvest Group Ltd. (BVT) ’s banking unit.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
